short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Image-Filter - Upload your photo and add set filters

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Image-Filter is an interactive extension where you can upload any personal image from your computer, add the filter of your choice and use it as your new wallpaper!

* By clicking "add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing Image-Filter new-tab extension and setting Chrome New Tab to that provider by the service and the EULA (https://image-filter.com/end-user-license-agreement/) and Policy (https://image-filter.com/privacy-policy/). The extension will update your search settings and will change your new tab and default search provider to Microsoft Bing.

For more information please visit our website.
